=========================================================================
                          DATABASES
=========================================================================
      
	Users
		id [int]				-> PRIMARY kEY
		name [varchar]
		age [int]
		gender [varchar]
		city [varchar]
		phone [long]
		email [varchar]			-> unique
		password [varchar]
	
	Accounts
		account_number [long]	-> PK 
		balance [double]
		security_pin [int]
		user_id [int] 			-> FOREIGN KEY (Users Table : id) 
		lock [boolean]
             
             
             

             
    
=========================================================================
                 FEATURES OF BANKING SYSTEM PROJECT
=========================================================================         
             
          
1. Register
2. Login
		case 1: If User Have Account 
		----------------------------
			1. Open a new Bank Account
			2. Log Out
		
		case 2: If User does not have Account
		-------------------------------------
			1. Profile Feature
				1. View User Details
				2. Update User Details
					1. Edit User Name
					2. Edit User Age
					3. Edit User City
					4. Edit Phone Number
					5. Return Back
				3. Return Back
			2. Banking Feature
				1. Check Balance
				2. View Account Details
				3. Debit Money (Withdraw)
				4. Credit Money (Deposit)
				5. Transfer Money
				6. Transaction History
				7. Return Back
			3. Security
				1. Change Login Password
				2. Change Security Pin
				3. Account Locking
				4. Account Unlocking
				5. Return Back
			4. Log Out
3. Exit  
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             